Without him, I would be dying; without him, how lost I would be.

00:38:01.853 --> 00:38:05.320
Jesus, do you know him today?

00:38:05.320 --> 00:38:08.440
Please don't turn him away.

00:38:08.440 --> 00:38:15.180
My precious Jesus, without him, how lost I would be.

00:38:15.180 --> 00:38:20.040
He inhabits the praises of his people.

00:38:20.040 --> 00:38:25.079
'Make a joyful noise unto the Lord.

00:38:25.079 --> 00:38:35.600
' So I do; I make a noise and I sing to him, and he comes and visits me.

00:38:35.600 --> 00:38:42.747
People say, 'How do you hear the Lord the way you do?

00:38:42.747 --> 00:38:46.680
' I make an atmosphere for him.

00:38:46.680 --> 00:38:51.712
God's more real to me than you are.

00:38:51.712 --> 00:38:53.453
He is my friend.

00:38:53.453 --> 00:38:58.200
I want so desperately for you to know him.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Intimacy comes over time.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
You develop a relationship with the Lord day by day.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
It starts out small and you keep growing.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
The Bible says, 'My sheep will know my voice and a stranger's voice they will not follow.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
' Stand on that scripture; claim that for yourself.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
You have to want it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
How bad do you want it?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
He's everything to me—more than air, more than your next meal.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
How desperate are you for him?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.700
If ye abide in me and my words abide in you, ye shall ask what ye will and it shall be done.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
Have the word of God deep down inside of your heart and ask him.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Use scripture in prayer.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
You do not need a prophetic voice; you have the Holy Spirit on the inside of you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
You have the ability to hear him for yourself.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
It just takes practice and endurance.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
I'm a work in progress.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
I work this out every single day.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
But whenever you start spending time with him, he'll become real to you and he'll start sharing the secret things.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
I hope this blessed you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
God bless you all.

